   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "QUESTIONS TO BE ANSWERED \n",
    "This project should help answer the following strategic questions: \n",
    "1. Are there distinct customer groups based on spending, income, engagement, and loyalty?\n",
    "2. What characteristics define each group? \n",
    "3. Which segments drive the most value to the business? \n",
    "4. Which segments show growth potential or churn risk? \n",
    "5. How can the business allocate resources differently across segments?\n"
   ]
  },
